{"tid":670302,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［疤痕植髮］有無巴打有相同經歷？方法？","createTime":"2018-05-19T08:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T10:08:36.000Z","uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"224f59a75cc82da95f7e147bfb81ca2e20988abc","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:45:40.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴打，我三個月前係頭縫針3針，問朋友話後面傷口位無左頭髮，個傷口疤痕仲好似後外變闊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有無人有疤痕植髮既經驗？<br />\n大概會要幾錢？<br />\n我只係個學生，但如果有好介紹，貴小小都可以。<br />\n我先20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我個位好細，大概母指甲大細到，會唔會因為咁，可以平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6000有無可能整好"},{"pid":"df5288811e28421a32b8565257bda6d88fd25030","tid":670302,"uid":76105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"手指甲咁細 ， 鬼會拎放大鏡睇你咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如果你生得靚仔，話知你光頭都靚仔㗎啦 <br />\n<br />\n除非你1米4啦 個個都睇到你頭殼頂。"},{"pid":"6cf46145cf07481b311190f5be37ce354c65dc1b","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"其實主要係因為有朋友話見到做位空左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e7db8dc3c91ac51be9edd1dbdd032590fccd9e","tid":670302,"uid":38798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf46145cf07481b311190f5be37ce354c65dc1b","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"其實主要係因為有朋友話見到做位空左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"照張相黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f463ac00467a2fd1942f38c1af910fa584065f01","tid":670302,"uid":81651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔做無疤果種？呢啲疤係一世咖喎，你成世要keep住後尾枕要留2-3cm"},{"pid":"0fc3dfd2d3c4a22f73d44e975e322bc39fc6b38c","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f463ac00467a2fd1942f38c1af910fa584065f01","tid":670302,"uid":81651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔做無疤果種？呢啲疤係一世咖喎，你成世要keep住後尾枕要留2-3cm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"咩黎？係咪講緊fue植髮？"},{"pid":"762351875b51c88f9cb10b48b5bafa4fcb00f268","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"其實最想知做呢類植髮手術價錢幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2-3cm傷口，要植既毛囊又大概會幾多<br />\n香港做會唔會有6-7000可以做好。"},{"pid":"f3e80382f44468eebe9655b025406777215c1996","tid":670302,"uid":81651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔做無疤果種？呢啲疤係一世咖喎，你成世要keep住後尾枕要留2-3cm</blockquote>咩黎？係咪講緊fue植髮？</blockquote><br />\n係啊fue,我講2-3cm係頭髮，你如果剷到好短會明顯有條坑，我係街見過一個人，佢應該植完髮，頭頂繼續惡化，結果佢放棄，成個頭剷到好短，好明顯有條疤痕"},{"pid":"7aaad476d338bf7b72aa3d7d3af7bae80b10f103","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"我自己都打算做fue<br />\n要拎既毛囊應該都唔會太多<br />\n更唔會有刀既疤痕"},{"pid":"8643a07db29690b1521add1feab46a58f5dc9ade","tid":670302,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3e80382f44468eebe9655b025406777215c1996","tid":670302,"uid":81651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔做無疤果種？呢啲疤係一世咖喎，你成世要keep住後尾枕要留2-3cm</blockquote>咩黎？係咪講緊fue植髮？</blockquote><br />\n係啊fue,我講2-3cm係頭髮，你如果剷到好短會明顯有條坑，我係街見過一個人，佢應該植完髮，頭頂繼續惡化，結果佢放棄，成個頭剷到好短，好明顯有條疤痕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"佢應該係真係有脫髮問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}